# Specification Authority

Document authority order: SGP.32 v1.3 + its ASN.1 module is what we build from. SGP.33-1 v1.1 defines conformant behavior and is the source for acceptance tests. SGP.22 supplies imported structures and the ES9+/ES8+ download flow. SGP.31 is background only. Where SGP.32 v1.3 and SGP.33-1 v1.1 conflict because the test spec is older, SGP.32 v1.3 wins and the conflict is logged in INTERPRETATION_LOG.md.

v1 implements Direct Profile Download only (device connects to SM-DP+). Indirect is deferred to v2.
